description: Welcome home to this spacious, corner residence on the 5th floor of The Macallen Bldg. The southwest exposure fills the space with natural light. The floor to ceiling windows in the main living space bring the city skyline right into the room affording great westerly views of the sunset as well.  Upon entering the condo, a gallery perfect for displaying artwork leads one down to the open concept living/dining/kitchen space which features an 8 ft long kitchen island, space for a large dining set and a large area for a full living room set.  A great entertaining space!  The oversized master suite has high end carpeting, plenty of closet space and an ensuite bath. The second bedroom is large enough to play double duty as both a home office and guest quarters.  In unit Miele washer/dryer, and one deeded garage pkg space included.  A second is being offered for $65,000.  24/7 concierge, gym, outdoor pool and BBQ area's! Seller welcomes offers with requests for buyer concessions.
